'''國際法經濟學評論'''（International Review of Law and Economics）是一本涵蓋[[法律|法律]]及[[經濟學|經濟學]]交叉學科的[[法律經濟學|法律經濟學]][[學術期刊|學術期刊]]，由[[律商联讯|律商联讯]]於1981年創辦，目前由[[愛思唯爾|愛思唯爾]]出版。[[總編輯|總編輯]]是伊曼紐拉·卡博納拉(Emanuela Carbonara；[[博洛尼亞大學|博洛尼亞大學]]）、張永健（[[中央研究院|中央研究院]]）<ref>"張永健(Yun-Chien Chang)"[https://www.iias.sinica.edu.tw/en/member_post/5] {{Wayback|url=https://www.iias.sinica.edu.tw/en/member_post/5 |date=20201208031708 }},IIAS 中央研究院法律學研究所,retrieved Marh 17,2021.</ref>、努諾·加魯帕（Nuno Garoupa；[[得克薩斯農工大學|得克薩斯農工大學]]及[[卡托利卡全球法學院|卡托利卡全球法學院]](Católica Global Law School)）、{{le|埃里克·海蘭德|Eric Helland}}（[[克萊蒙特·麥肯納學院|克萊蒙特·麥肯納學院]]）以及{{le|喬納森·克里克|Jonathan Klick}}（[[賓夕法尼亞大學|賓夕法尼亞大學]]）。根據《[[期刊引證報告|期刊引證報告]]》，該期刊在2019年的[[影響因子|影響因子]]為⟨0.806⟩；{{le|引證評量|CiteScore}}為⟨1.1⟩。<ref name=WoS>{{cite book |year=2017 |chapter=International Review of Law and Economics |title=2016 Journal Citation Reports |publisher=[[Thomson_Reuters|Thomson Reuters]] |edition=Science |series=[[Web_of_Science|Web of Science]]|title-link=Journal Citation Reports }}</ref><ref name=2019ifcs/>

在2021年，[[美國|美國]][[哈佛大學法學院|哈佛大學法學院]][[教授|教授]]{{le|約翰·馬克·拉姆塞耶|John Mark Ramseyer}}[https://hls.harvard.edu/faculty/directory/10697/Ramseyer] {{Wayback|url=https://hls.harvard.edu/faculty/directory/10697/Ramseyer |date=20210308072450 }}預定2021年3月在本評論發表一篇論文「太平洋戰爭中的性契約(Contracting for Sex in the Pacific War)」<ref>{{cite journal|title=Contracting for sex in the Pacific War |journal=International Review of Law and Economics |volume=65 |date=March 2021 |first=J. Mark |last= Ramseyer |doi=10.1016/j.irle.2020.105971}}</ref>，評論的[[同行評審|同行評審]]過程受到質疑。<ref>Jeannie Suk Gersen,"Seeking the True Story of the Comfort Women"[https://www.newyorker.com/culture/annals-of-inquiry/seeking-the-true-story-of-the-comfort-women-j-mark-ramseyer] {{Wayback|url=https://www.newyorker.com/culture/annals-of-inquiry/seeking-the-true-story-of-the-comfort-women-j-mark-ramseyer |date=20210321165309 }}, The New Yorker,February 25, 2021.</ref><ref>Youmi Kim and Mike Ives,"A Harvard Professor Called Wartime Sex Slaves ‘Prostitutes.’ One Pushed Back."[https://www.nytimes.com/2021/02/26/world/asia/harvard-professor-comfort-women.html] {{Wayback|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2021/02/26/world/asia/harvard-professor-comfort-women.html |date=20210312082057 }},The New York Times,Feb. 26, 2021.</ref>在該篇文章中，作者從不存在的[[合同|合同]]中提出了反對意見，聲稱[[日本帝國|日本帝國]]時代被迫淪為[[性奴隸|性奴隸]]的[[慰安婦|慰安婦]]是出於自願[[性交易|賣淫]]。<ref>{{Cite journal|url=https://www.newyorker.com/culture/annals-of-inquiry/seeking-the-true-story-of-the-comfort-women-j-mark-ramseyer|title=Seeking the True Story of the Comfort Women|author=Jeannie Suk Gersen|date=2021-02-26|journal=The New Yorker|language=en-US|access-date=2021-02-26|archive-date=2021-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210321165309/https://www.newyorker.com/culture/annals-of-inquiry/seeking-the-true-story-of-the-comfort-women-j-mark-ramseyer}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2021/02/26/world/asia/harvard-professor-comfort-women.html|title=A Harvard Professor Called Wartime Sex Slaves ‘Prostitutes.’ One Pushed Back.|author=Youmi Kim and Mike Ives|date=2021-02-26|journal=The New York Times|language=en-US|access-date=2021-02-26|archive-date=2021-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210312082057/https://www.nytimes.com/2021/02/26/world/asia/harvard-professor-comfort-women.html}}</ref><ref>編輯:馮昭,"哈佛教授主張慰安婦自願賣淫 費城議會通過譴責"[https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202103060104.aspx] {{Wayback|url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202103060104.aspx |date=20210310161452 }},中央通訊社,2021-03-06.</ref><ref>國際,"哈佛教授稱慰安婦自願賣淫 南韓學生要求道歉撤文"[https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3437285] {{Wayback|url=https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3437285 |date=20210301123259 }},自由時報電子報,2021/02/10.</ref><ref>澎湃号·媒体,"哈佛教授称"慰安妇是自愿卖淫"，韩外交部这回应…"[https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_11386542] {{Wayback|url=https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_11386542 |date=20210227115857 }},澎湃新闻,2021-02-19.</ref>

